casebody.data:
Robert Lee Johnson v. Warden, Connecticut Correctional Institute (6508)

Dupont, C. J., O’Connell and Norcott, Js.

Argued November 17 decision released December 13, 1988 Ernest J. Diette, Jr., special public defender, for the appellant (petitioner). Julia DiCocco Dewey, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, was Steven Sellers, deputy assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (respondent). Per Curiam.

There is no error.
